  <brief_title>Efficacy of &quot;Tailored Physical Activity&quot; in Health Care Workers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of &quot;Tailored Physical Activity&quot; on the Number of Sick Days: a Randomized Controlled Trial in Health Care Workers That Have Experienced Pain Related to the Spine or Upper Body</official_title>
